Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.4.3
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: RootHide iOS 16 overlap and Settings repair. Generates preference controls directly in code, treats the iOS 16 Lists to Contacts stack as a root screen, hosts each custom tab in one opaque isolated container, restores the complete Apple screen when a custom tab is disabled, and preserves stock contact details and active-call controllers.
Maintainer: Next Solution
Author: Next Solution
Section: Tweaks
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
